SHEET 1 1200 680
* =============================================================================
* Jensen JT-115K-E — LTspice reference model
*
* Line input transformer, 1:10 turns ratio.
* Core: Mu-Metal 80% NiFe (EI lamination)
*
* Electrical parameters (from datasheet + jensen_jt115ke.json):
*   Rdc_primary   = 19.7 Ohm
*   Rdc_secondary = 2465 Ohm
*   Lp (primary)  = 10 H (estimated at low-level)
*   L_leakage     = 1 mH
*   C_interwinding = 10 pF
*   C_sec_shield  = 205 pF
*   Source Z       = 150 Ohm
*   Load Z         = 150 kOhm
*
* Frequency response targets:
*   -0.5 dB @ 20 Hz
*   -0.2 dB @ 20 kHz
*   -3 dB  @ 140 kHz
*   CMRR   ~ 110 dB @ 60 Hz
*
* THD targets:
*   0.065% @ 20 Hz, -20 dBu
*   1.0%   @ 20 Hz, -2.5 dBu
*   4.0%   @ 20 Hz, +1.2 dBu
*
* Reference: Jensen Transformers datasheet; Transfo_Model v3
* =============================================================================
